%footer
  .row-fluid
    .span2
      %img(src="/assets/frontend/sn-logo.png" alt="Software Niagara")

    .span4
      %h6
        About
      %p
        The Software Niagara website is actively developed by a group of volunteers.
        %a(href="/about/")
          Learn More
      %p
        The code is open source and available at
        != "#{link_to 'Github', 'https://github.com/softwareniagara/software-niagara'}."
        Send us a pull request if you want to help out with the site.

    .span4
      %h6
        Credits
      %ul
        %li
          Banner image photographed by
          %a(href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/kevlar/")
            Kevin Baird
        %li
          Logo donated by
          %a(href="http://www.leighannfrommann.com/")
            LeighAnn Frommann

      %p
        != "&copy; #{Time.now.strftime('%Y')} Software Niagara. All rights reserved."

    .span2
      %p
        Follow us:
      .row-fluid
        .span5
          %a(href="http://twitter.com/softwareniagara" title="Follow us on Twitter")
            %img(src="/assets/frontend/twitter_logo.png")

        .span1

        .span5.pull-right
          %a(href="http://www.facebook.com/softwareniagara" title="Follow us on Facebook")
            %img(src="/assets/frontend/facebook_logo.png")